channel.title: Alex Isle 317 Client + Source + STAFF OF LIGHT!
channel.description:
Hello, this is the first source i am releasing and prob my last 317 one. (But you never know :D) Enjoy!
Download: http://uploading.com/files/5e1939m5/Alex%2BIsle%2BV2.8%2BClient%2Band%2BSource.rar/ 47.76 MB (Source + Client)
Credits:
Tehlife (me) The guy who made Riverside ElitePk
Stuff i added:
Staff of light New skill called M.K (monster killing) witch has it own godsword and teleport witch you can tele in lunar and ancient. Monster killing skillcape (witch was first called 'death cape' I added alot of models that are in Runescape right now. Example: New Dharoks axe model. Added new mining guild and smithing guild. New skill place. New teleport place. Npc walking. [u][b][i]NEW WILDERNESS NEAR HOME!!!![/i][/b][/u]
Note: [b][i][u]If you gonna use this source as your server and put online tell me![/u][/i][/b]
Pictures:
Starter & login screen when you start! [img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/7796/0057n.png[/img] Home! [img]http://img155.imageshack.us/img155/3531/0024g.png[/img] Mining Guild made 100% by me! [img]http://img20.imageshack.us/img20/282/0023dp.png[/img] Some fishing shop. [img]http://img191.imageshack.us/img191/1508/0036a.png[/img] New Dharok Model! [img]http://img338.imageshack.us/img338/8471/0030m.png[/img] New Whip Model! [img]http://img822.imageshack.us/img822/4411/0068.png[/img] Cool fletching! [img]http://img84.imageshack.us/img84/8428/0033.png[/img] 100% Clan Chat! [img]http://img269.imageshack.us/img269/4302/0047.png[/img] Portals that teleport you to bosses! [img]http://img823.imageshack.us/img823/3140/0054.png[/img] Fishing! [img]http://img337.imageshack.us/img337/4760/0052.png[/img] Login screen! [img]http://img227.imageshack.us/img227/2619/0022.png[/img] [b][i][u]STAFF OF LIGHT![/u][/i][/b] [img]http://img23.imageshack.us/img23/5325/00332y.png[/img] Pvp area! [img]http://img217.imageshack.us/img217/5345/0031.png[/img] New Donater sympol.... [img]http://img441.imageshack.us/img441/82/0034.png[/img] Slayer tower.... [img]http://img62.imageshack.us/img62/33/0050.png[/img] Woodcutting! (there are alot of more places, like yew) [img]http://img215.imageshack.us/img215/7449/0053.png[/img] Another woodcut place! [img]http://img229.imageshack.us/img229/7373/0051k.png[/img] Pvp teleport! Home pking teles you to the new wilderness! (Ofcourse the old one works fine still) [img]http://img16.imageshack.us/img16/6747/0300o.png[/img] Walking npcs! [img]http://img707.imageshack.us/img707/4562/0028r.png[/img] Some Shop! [img]http://img130.imageshack.us/img130/6385/0035k.png[/img] 100% Monster killing! [img]http://img808.imageshack.us/img808/5931/0059.png[/img]
Download: http://uploading.com/files/5e1939m5/Alex%2BIsle%2BV2.8%2BClient%2Band%2BSource.rar/ 47.76 MB (Source + Client)
Enjoy
